Day03
------------

How to specify Path and Query Parameter

1. https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/todos?userId=1
2. https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/todos?userId=1&id=7

https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com - DOMAIN
todos = PATH
After ? userId=1 = QUERY


Path param  - we have to define as a key,value pair and mention the name of key inside the url
query param - we have to simply define as a key, value pair, no need to mention

